spec_data.Name: bluez
spec_data.Description:
Utilities for use in Bluetooth applications:
	- hcitool
	- hciattach
	- hciconfig
	- bluetoothd
	- l2ping
	- rfcomm
	- sdptool
	- bccmd
	- bluetoothctl
	- btmon
	- hcidump
	- l2test
	- rctest
	- gatttool
	- start scripts (Red Hat)
	- pcmcia configuration files

The BLUETOOTH trademarks are owned by Bluetooth SIG, Inc., U.S.A.
